@startuml Backend persistence modes

left to right direction

rectangle "Program.cs" as Program
rectangle "RecipeService" as Service
interface "IRecipeRepository" as Repo

database "Memory mode" as MemoryMode
database "File mode\nApp_Data/recipes.json" as FileMode
database "Sqlite mode\nApp_Data/recipes.db" as SqliteMode

rectangle "RecipeDbContext" as DbContext
rectangle "RecipeDbInitializer" as DbInitializer

Program --> Service
Service --> Repo

Repo <|.. MemoryMode
Repo <|.. FileMode
Repo <|.. SqliteMode

SqliteMode --> DbContext
Program --> DbInitializer
DbInitializer --> DbContext

note bottom of Program
Val via appsettings:
- Memory
- File
- Sqlite
end note

note right of SqliteMode
Aktivt standardlage i
appsettings.Development.json
end note

note left of MemoryMode
Anvands som stabil baseline
och i endpointtester
end note

@enduml
